        "body": "Controllers: Refactored and updated logic for appointments, authentication, reviews, and services.\r\nRoutes: Updated route files to improve structure and error handling.\r\nMiddleware: Added a global error handler to catch and respond to errors consistently.\r\nServer Entry: Created/updated server/app.js to initialize the server, connect to MongoDB, and set up middleware and routes.\r\nPackage Files: Updated package.json and package-lock.json to reflect new dependencies or scripts as needed.\r\nTesting\r\nServer starts successfully and connects to MongoDB.\r\nAll routes respond as expected.\r\nErrors are handled gracefully and return appropriate responses.\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **New Features**\n  * Introduced a centralized error handling system for consistent and user-friendly error responses.\n  * Added a new server application setup with improved environment configuration and database connectivity.\n\n* **Bug Fixes**\n  * Standardized error propagation across authentication, appointment, service, and review features for more reliable error reporting.\n\n* **Chores**\n  * Upgraded dependencies for improved stability and security.\n\n* **Documentation**\n  * Enhanced route comments for clarity and readability, including improved formatting and emoji annotations.\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
