        },
        "body": "This pull request improves the Google Sign-In authentication flow for the Fix-Time MERN app by addressing error handling and validation on both the frontend and backend:\r\nFrontend (React)\r\nEnhanced error handling for Google Sign-In:\r\nChecks for missing or invalid credentials before attempting to decode.\r\nDisplays specific error messages from the backend to the user.\r\nProvides user feedback for common Google login issues.\r\nBackend (Express)\r\nImproved validation and logging in the Google login controller:\r\nLogs incoming request data for easier debugging.\r\nValidates that all required fields (email, name, sub) are present.\r\nChecks for the presence of JWT_SECRET and returns a clear error if missing.\r\nProvides more detailed error messages for troubleshooting.",
